{"TopicId":129638,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"To level up Kerbals, can I plant a flag and take it down?","CreatedByName":"Chaos_Evolved","CreatedById":108522,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-01-10T15:45:13Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Chaos_Evolved","CreatedById":108522,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-01-10T15:45:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m asking for clarification with regards to leveling. The wiki says:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Experience\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Experience\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf only one Kerbal in the mission plants a flag, only that Kerbal will gain experience for having done so. \u003Cstrong\u003EThe kerbonaut gains the experience and reaches level only when it returns to the \u003Ca href=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Astronaut_Complex\u0022 title=\u0022Astronaut Complex\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EAstronaut Complex\u003C/a\u003E by \u003Ca href=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Recovery\u0022 title=\u0022Recovery\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Erecovery\u003C/a\u003E. \u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe line in bold makes it ambiguous as to whether the flag has to stay planted on a particular surface. I\u0027m asking because A) I don\u0027t want dozens of flags everywhere and B ) ideally I would prefer doing a multi-flag-planting run in one launch. Perhaps someone ought to clarify this in the wiki.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo do the flags have to stay there to get the xp? I take it for granted that they can be taken down after arriving back on kerbin; I\u0027m asking if they can be taken down right after being planted.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Laie","CreatedById":110461,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-01-10T17:01:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes. You can level up a shipload of Kerbals by each one going EVA, planting a flag, taking it down, going back inside, NEXT!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Chaos_Evolved","CreatedById":108522,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-01-10T17:06:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222355804\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022129638\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221452445314\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110461\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Laie\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, Laie said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes. You can level up a shipload of Kerbals by each one going EVA, planting a flag, taking it down, going back inside, NEXT!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthanks\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alshain","CreatedById":110959,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-01-10T17:10:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222355804\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022129638\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221452445314\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110461\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Laie\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 minutes ago, Laie said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes. You can level up a \u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Eshipload\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E of Kerbals by each one going EVA, planting a flag, taking it down, going back inside, NEXT!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI totally misread that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-01-10T20:45:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222355818\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022129638\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221452445848\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110959\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Alshain\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Alshain said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI totally misread that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe great part is, it works either way.\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}